id: pm-qyc6
title: "GH-558: export canonical item-to-context-relevance candidate derivation from the public SDK"
description: "Promote the existing CLI-owned item signal derivation into a stable public SDK primitive so extensions reproduce pm next/context ranking without deep imports, subprocesses, or drift."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 1
tags[5]: "area:sdk",context,extensions,gh-issue,relevance
